%% Communications Ledger — Communication Lifecycle
%% Active -> Resolved? -> Promote (Decisions / Open Problems / Box) or Archive

flowchart LR
    Created["Entry created<br/>COMM-YYYY-MM-DD-###"] --> Active["Active<br/>(Sections 4-9)"]:::active

    Active --> ReadCheck{Read by a<br/>future agent?}
    ReadCheck -->|Yes, useful| Apply["Agent applies<br/>the message"]:::active
    ReadCheck -->|Yes, no longer relevant| ResolveStart["Mark for resolution"]
    ReadCheck -->|Periodic review| StaleCheck{Still<br/>relevant?}
    StaleCheck -->|Yes| Active
    StaleCheck -->|No| ResolveStart

    Apply --> Outcome{Outcome shifts<br/>the entry?}
    Outcome -->|Becomes a settled rule| PromoteDec["Promote to<br/>Decisions Ledger"]:::promote
    Outcome -->|Becomes a tracked problem| PromoteOP["Promote to<br/>Open Problems Ledger"]:::promote
    Outcome -->|Becomes local context| MoveBox["Move to local Box"]:::promote
    Outcome -->|Still active| Active

    ResolveStart --> Reason{Why resolved?}
    Reason -->|Promoted| PromoteDec
    Reason -->|Promoted| PromoteOP
    Reason -->|Promoted| MoveBox
    Reason -->|No longer applies| Archive["Section 10<br/>Archived"]:::archive

    PromoteDec --> Marker["Original entry marked<br/>status: promoted<br/>+ pointer to new home"]
    PromoteOP --> Marker
    MoveBox --> Marker
    Marker --> ArchiveAfter["Archive after one<br/>session cycle confirms<br/>the promotion sticks"]:::archive
    Archive --> ArchiveAfter

    classDef active fill:#10b981,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
    classDef promote fill:#7c3aed,stroke:#5b21b6,color:#fff
    classDef archive fill:#9ca3af,stroke:#4b5563,color:#fff
